# DESCRIPTION
# A first problem looking at subspaces
# ENDDESCRIPTION

##\{ textbook_ref_exact("Holt Linear Algebra", "4.1","3") \}
## DBsubject(Linear algebra)
## DBchapter(Euclidean spaces)
## DBsection(Subspaces)
## Institution(Saint Louis University)
## Author(Mike May)
## Level(3)
## TitleText1('Linear Algebra')
## AuthorText1('Holt')
## EditionText1('')
## Section1('4.1')
